reviewText: I absolutely love Thomas and Friends. Watch Thomas DVD's all the time. They are fabulous.
my grandson's love Thomas and they will watch the same shows over and over again without getting bored, very entertaining

my 2 yrs old daughter loves thomas the train she calls him choo choo
very happy with the product

Story stops are:

1.  Molly's Special Special
2.  Respect For Gordon
3.  Emily Knows Best
4.  Saving Edward
5.  Rheneas And The Dinosaur
6.  Thomas, Percy And The Golden Eagle
